snippet.title: Action Reload
snippet.description:
Action Reload is THE destination for high-quality action scenes on YouTube. From shootouts, car chases, and martial arts fights, we have the best action sequences from modern cinema. Featuring action icons like Jason Statham, Scott Adkins, Donnie Yen & Sylvester Stallone. 

Action Reload is made possible through our partnerships with a number of production and distribution companies. All the content showcased on the channel has been properly licenced and has been geo-restricted to the corresponding territories. If, however, you still see uploads that you believe infringes your rights, please contact us at copyright@lassogroup.com and our team will get in touch with you swiftly.
